1. On je čudo *čuda* radosti! (He is a miracle of joy!)
2. U njoj je čudo *čuda* ljubavi! (In her, there is a miracle of love!)
3. Činio je čuda *čudo* na zemlji! (He performed miracles on earth!)
4. Ona je čudo *čudo* prirode! (She is a miracle of nature!)
5. On je čudo *čudo* koje je stvorio Bog! (He is a miracle created by God!)